Drive For Us
 
Heartland Express drivers are known for being the best in the businessCall Recruiting at (888) 919-1812 Apply Now


Heartland Express drivers are the key to the success of the company. Our drivers are known to be some of the best in the business. As a result, Heartland offers one of the most attractive driving positions, backed by a commitment to safety and better driver CSA scores, a commitment to keeping drivers busy and productive, a commitment to meeting home-time promises, and the very best pay available. Earn up to 55 cpm!Excellent home timenew equipment







































HEARTLAND EXPRESS IS PROUD TO BE A CORPORATE SPONSOR FOR TRUCKERS AGAINST TRAFFICKING.ABOUT TRUCKERS AGAINST TRAFFICKING  







Modern-day slavery, or human trafficking exists whenever people are bought and sold for forced labor or commercial sex. Around the world, there are an estimated 20.9 million slaves today. Human trafficking has been reported in all 50 states, and the number of victims in the United States is estimated in the hundreds of thousands. While illegal, human trafficking is a booming business. Traffickers recruit out of our schools, online, in shopping malls, as well as the streets and other locations. A large percentage of the people trafficked are women and children. Many of them are used in the sex industry. They are the prostituted people on the street and in private homes, and in legitimate businesses such as restaurants, truck stops and motels. They need to be identified and rescued.  Visit Website > MAKE THE CALL. SAVE LIVES.1-888-373-7888










Services
 
The top shippers in America depend on Heartland Express

SCROLL DOWN





Services
 
The top shippers in America depend on Heartland Express


Heartland Express brings together industry experience, state of the art equipment and technology, and good people with a vision to be the best, to serve the truckload transportation needs of the top shippers in America. Our services improve the daily lives of people by moving goods and supplies to where they are needed, to the super-market shelves, to the manufacturing production lines, to the home improvement stores in our communities. Long haul truckload transportationWith a large fleet of over the road drivers, we provide truckload transportation service to virtually all markets east of the Rocky Mountains at any length of haul. Regional truckload transportationWith operating centers located in key markets nation-wide, our regional operations serve the short to medium haul needs of shippers (see who we serve), ranging from local shuttle operations to one or two day transits. Loads are executed by regionally based drivers, customer service, dispatch managers, and shop maintenance facilities. Team and Dedicated OperationsThese specialized divisions allow us to provide continuous service on long length of haul loads to the West Coast and the Northwest, as well as other regions. We also provide dedicated tour or round-trip oriented service in various markets nation-wide.REQUEST A RATETo request a rate or ask questions, please contact our Sales Department at (800) 451-4621. 










Industry Solutions
 
Delivering exceptional results to our customers

SCROLL DOWN





Industry Solutions
 
Delivering exceptional results to our customers


Heartland Express customers represent the most successful businesses in the world. The top shippers in America depend on Heartland Express to improve business performance, deliver exceptional results to their customers, and drive overall value into their transportation supply chain. AUTOMOTIVEAs the performance needs of our shippers increase, Heartland Express has even more opportunity to differentiate our service and demonstrate the strength that our company was built on.  FedEx and other top shippers have recently awarded Heartland as their carrier of the year.







CONSUMER GOODSAnother consistent contributor to the economy, we appreciate the opportunity to serve our customers in the consumer goods space.  Unilever and other leaders in the consumer goods market have recently awarded Heartland Express as their best-in-class performer. 







FOODAs an essential and consistent segment of the American economy, food distribution makes up a substantial portion of the customers we serve.  Heartland Express has been honored to accept performance awards recently from Quaker Oats, Gatorade, Kellogg Company, Nestle Waters, and many more. 







MANUFACTURINGHeartland Express serves the supply chain needs of many manufacturers in America, including supply operations, DC transfers, and vendor deliveries.  As supply-to-cash cycles get shorter and faster in the JIT environment, Heartland has excelled in meeting difficult requirements.  Whirlpool and other leading producers have recently recognized Heartland Express as their supplier of the year. 







PAPER AND PLASTICWe serve many shippers that manufacturer and supply paper, plastic, and packaging products.  Cups, bowls, plates, containers, napkins, tissues, home and office paper - some of the many products that our drivers protect and deliver every day.   







RETAILHeartland Express excels at time-sensitive store replenishment, and has recently won performance awards from Sears, Walmart, Lowes, and many more.  We value this business and the strategic relationships that we have developed to execute for the retailers that we serve. 







Request a RateTo request a rate or have questions please contact our Sales Department at 800-451-4621. 































