			Company Description 


			Heartland Express, Inc. operates as a holding company, which engages in the provision of short-to-medium haul truckload carrier services. Its activities include long haul truckload and regional truckload transportation; on-time pick up and delivery, and industry solutions. The company was founded by...
		


                Heartland Express, Inc. operates as a holding company, which engages in the provision of short-to-medium haul truckload carrier services. Its activities include long haul truckload and regional truckload transportation; on-time pick up and delivery, and industry solutions. The company was founded by Russell A. Gerdin in 1978 and is headquartered in North Liberty, IA.
            




